descriptions.see_description: In the input, you should see...an area of red blocks with an area of black blocks
descriptions.grid_description: The output grid size...stays the same
descriptions.do_description: To make the output, you have to...fill the black boxes with green

descriptions.see_description: In the input, you should see...a number of boxes with holes in them
descriptions.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same as the input
descriptions.do_description: To make the output, you have to...fill in the holes of the boxes with green, then black out the outlines of the boxes
